{"tid":315570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強姦犯又上吊？","createTime":"2017-07-10T06:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T06:50:26.000Z","uid":79817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6fc2b0f65c58a20c0d590d9c60204fcc9d49084","tid":315570,"uid":79817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/143502_52aaabd9aaf92b9074e011e9d828b376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F143502_52aaabd9aaf92b9074e011e9d828b376.jpg&h=2f1b3d2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2349763327ec59cfd60320e8ffc94e69de067b90","tid":315570,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:36:24.000Z","msg":"最撚興嫁啦"},{"pid":"88ea93cd72cef1e67787e224198e020beef3de8e","tid":315570,"uid":79817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"今晨8時半，荔枝角收押所的保安員，發現一名還柙的男子，在活動室的窗邊吊頸企圖自殺。職員連忙將他解下，召救護車將他送明愛醫院，再通知警方。據了解，事主涉及上月中一宗風化案，被還押看守。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署回覆查詢稱，職員今日在荔枝角收押所制止一名28歲男性還押在囚人士上吊自殺。早上8時01分，懲教員發現該名在囚人士於日間活動室廁所內的窗框用床單上吊，於是立即召喚支援並進行急救。他當時昏迷，其後被轉送至公立醫院作進一步治療。懲教署已將案件通知警方。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署發言人表示：「本署一直採取一切可行措施，包括行政安排、改良院所設施、職員培訓及急救護理等，以防止在囚人士自殺或作出自殘行為。」該名在囚人士因強姦罪而還押候審。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，吊頸男子涉嫌於上月9日，在寶田邨尾隨一名女住客乘搭升降機回家，其間色魔提早出𨋢，跑樓梯到女事主住所外守候，趁她離家外出時，將她推入屋內強姦。警方接報追緝3日在旺角拘捕疑犯。﹝ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2u304Wr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2u304Wr&d=X%2By74uZZfd73voHFVcoF4wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2f0fc13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2u304Wr</a> ﹞"},{"pid":"6d7bbb11e8bbd2ba6d1f18277408dd4a33c2dff7","tid":315570,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"法律係制裁唔到呢d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4230e9a1b89b5c7380fdc2b058b8da6b955228","tid":315570,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"神憎鬼厭"},{"pid":"6ed5c48dbe14a72b0b7e624adfe1ee2b6da26d26","tid":315570,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:50:26.000Z","msg":"死亡筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}